# OneRF — ecossistema e documentação

**Modelo de produto:** Backend IoT + Analytics IoT (plataformas **transversais**) + HUB APPs (apps **segmentadas**).

Antes de implementar ou rever código em **qualquer** repo OneRF:

1. **Docs comuns (SSOT):** [onerf-platform-docs/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/README.md)
2. **Ecossistema:** [ECOSYSTEM.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/ECOSYSTEM.md)
3. **Visão estruturante:** [platform/PLATFORM_VISION.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/platform/PLATFORM_VISION.md)

## Por repositório

| Camada | Repo | Índice |
|--------|------|--------|
| Backend IoT (transversal) | `backend` | [products/backend-iot/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/products/backend-iot/README.md) |
| Analytics IoT (transversal) | `b2b_analytics` | [products/analytics/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/products/analytics/README.md) |
| HUB APPs (segmento) | KlabinDash, SinterDash, SolarDash, AppHub | [products/hub-apps/README.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/products/hub-apps/README.md) |

## Regras

- Backend IoT e Analytics IoT são **transversais** — evitar regras de um segmento no core.
- HUB APPs são **finas** — consomem API das plataformas; metadado de segmento no repo da app.
- Contrato HTTP: [platform/API_CONTRACT.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/platform/API_CONTRACT.md).
- Integração plataformas: [platform/INTEGRATION_PATTERNS.md](../../onerf-platform-docs/platform/INTEGRATION_PATTERNS.md).
- ADR-001: sem MQTT inter-sistema.
